# GIGASHIELD NEXUS ENTERPRISE — Complete Implementation Blueprint

> **Version**: 2.0 | **Updated**: 2026-03-18
> **Target**: Guidewire DevTrails Hackathon — 20,000+ competitors
> **Judge Score Target**: 22/25 (Innovation 4.5 + Tech 4.5 + Impact 4.5 + Feasibility 4 + Presentation 4.5)

---

## 1. SYSTEM OVERVIEW

### 1.1 What We're Building
An AI-powered parametric microinsurance platform that automatically detects external disruptions (weather, pollution, civic events), validates claims using physics-based fraud detection, and disburses income-loss payouts to gig delivery workers within 3 minutes — all built natively on Guidewire Cloud Platform.

### 1.2 Why We Win
- **Only team building ON Guidewire** (not beside it) — judges are Guidewire employees
- **Shield-SAC**: First DRL-based pricing with mathematically guaranteed fairness constraints
- **PADS**: Physics-based fraud detection using IMU kinematics (not just GPS)
- **DSI**: Composite Disruption Severity Index replacing simplistic binary triggers
- **WhatsApp-first**: Zero app-download onboarding in regional languages
- **Shield Pools**: Community micro-insurance reducing premiums 15-20%

