| **ML Utilities** | Scikit-learn, SHAP, NumPy, SciPy | Latest | Anomaly detection, XAI, PADS kinematics |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL | 16+ | Guidewire-native; JSONB for flexible data |
| **Cache** | Redis | 7+ | DSI score caching, session management |
| **Message Queue** | Apache Kafka (or Redis Streams) | 3.7+ | App Events stream; trigger → claim pipeline |
