| **Weather API** | OpenWeatherMap (free tier) | 3.0 | Real-time weather data for 5 cities |
| **Container** | Docker + Docker Compose | 24+ | Local dev + deployment |
| **Orchestration** | Kubernetes (basic) | 1.28+ | Demo scaling narrative |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions | Latest | Automated build → test → deploy |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana | Latest | System health; demo metric dashboards |

